data.description: Near Elk River Gem: Home with Solar Elegance in Noel, Missouri! Your Future Awaits in This 3BR/2BA Solar-Powered Haven! Picture a spacious home bathed in natural light, where original hardwood floors exude warmth, and skylights invite the sun's rays. This delightful residence offers more than comfort; it offers a promise of sustainable living with fully paid solar panels. Nestled on over half an acre, this property is just a short drive away from the enchanting Elk River. Imagine weekend adventures, fishing, and leisurely strolls along the riverbanks. Recent updates include new windows, siding, and a roof  installed in 2022, ensuring peace of mind for years to come.
